OL,3,C'I trusted them': Kent mum on
OL,4,Cdisgraced surgeon who left son in
OL,5,Clifelong pain
OL,7,FA mother from Kent has spoken of her
OL,8,Fheartbreak after her teenage son was
OL,9,Fleft in constant pain following
OL,10,Ftreatment by a disgraced surgeon at
OL,11,FGreat Ormond Street Hospital (GOSH).
OL,13,FRyan Kelly, now 19, from Chatham, was
OL,14,Fborn with a club foot. While he knew
OL,15,Fit would never work perfectly, his
OL,16,Ffamily say they were promised by
OL,17,Fpaediatric orthopaedic surgeon Yaser
OL,18,FJabbar that surgery would make his
OL,19,Ffoot functional.
