OL,3,C'I trusted them': Kent mum on
OL,4,Cdisgraced surgeon who left son in
OL,5,Clifelong pain
OL,7,FInstead, Ryan was left with a deformed
OL,8,Ftibia, a misaligned ankle and foot,
OL,9,Fand constant pain after what his
OL,10,Ffamily say were botched operations and
OL,11,Fan early discharge from hospital.
OL,13,FAn internal investigation by GOSH
OL,14,Ffound that of nearly 800 children
OL,15,Ftreated by Jabbar over five years, 94
OL,16,Fwere harmed - including 36 severely
OL,17,Fand 39 moderately. The report also
OL,18,Funcovered missing consent forms and
OL,19,Fcases where procedures carried out did
OL,20,Fnot match what families had agreed to.
