OL,3,C'I trusted them': Kent mum on
OL,4,Cdisgraced surgeon who left son in
OL,5,Clifelong pain
OL,7,FSpeaking exclusively to ITV News
OL,8,FMeridian, Ryan's mother Susan said the
OL,9,Ftrauma has left her son fearful of
OL,10,Fmedical treatment and largely
OL,11,Fhousebound.
OL,13,F"To go into somewhere like Great
OL,14,FOrmond Street, it felt like a massive
OL,15,Fachievement for us," she said. "You
OL,16,Fbelieve they're going to fix your
OL,17,Fchild."
OL,19,FSusan said he now refuses to see a GP
OL,20,For dentist and is deeply hesitant
OL,21,Fabout further treatment.
