OL,3,C'I trusted them': Kent mum on
OL,4,Cdisgraced surgeon who left son in
OL,5,Clifelong pain
OL,7,F"It's heartbreaking," she said. "The
OL,8,Fguilt I live with ` as a parent, I
OL,9,Ffeel like I failed my child. I trusted
OL,10,Fthe surgeon I was referred to. Mum
OL,11,Fguilt is hard."
OL,13,FAsked what she would say to him now,
OL,14,FSusan said: "You didn't need to do
OL,15,Fthis. You could have put your hands up
OL,16,Fand said, 'I don't know.' Instead,
OL,17,Fyou've left children like mine going
OL,18,Finto adulthood with severe pain and
OL,19,Fpsychological damage. I just want to
OL,20,Fknow why this was allowed to go on for
OL,21,Fso long."
