OL,3,C'I trusted them': Kent mum on
OL,4,Cdisgraced surgeon who left son in
OL,5,Clifelong pain
OL,7,FGOSH's chief executive Matthew Shaw
OL,8,Fapologised to families, admitting the
OL,9,Fhospital had breached their trust.
OL,11,F"Yaser Jabbar's practice was
OL,12,Fcompletely unacceptable," he said.
OL,13,F"There are reasons, but there are no
OL,14,Fexcuses. I am deeply and profoundly
OL,15,Fsorry for all the children and
OL,16,Ffamilies who have come to harm."
