OL,3,C'I trusted them': Kent mum on
OL,4,Cdisgraced surgeon who left son in
OL,5,Clifelong pain
OL,7,FThe Department for Health & Social
OL,8,FCare says its working with NHS England
OL,9,Fon its own investigation into
OL,10,Fpotential failures of leadership at
OL,11,Fthe hospital.
OL,13,FLawyers are now supporting affected
OL,14,Ffamilies like Ryan's with clinical
OL,15,Fnegligence claims. Jabbar, who now
OL,16,Flives abroad, no longer holds a
OL,17,Flicence to practise medicine in the UK
OL,18,Fand told ITV News he cannot comment
OL,19,Fdue to an ongoing investigation.
